These are Puzzles for 4x4 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-8-1::.
There are 4 different nationalities: american, australian, turkish, british
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: r&b, disco, reggae, electronic
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: cycling, ice-hockey, lacrosse, water-polo
City: colone, berlin, marseilles, london
 1. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is not to the right of the person who's sport is cycling##8
 2. the person traveling to colone is not to the left of the person traveling to colone##8
 3. the person traveling to london is on the far left or far right##3
 4. the person who's sport is cycling is not to the left of the person who's sport is water-polo##8
 5. the person traveling to colone is not to the right of the person traveling to colone##8
 6. the fan of reggae is on the right of the person who's sport is water-polo##1
 7. the australian is somewhere to the right of the american##5
 8. the fan of electronic is between the person traveling to berlin and the person who's sport is ice-hockey##2
 9. the person traveling to london is the fan of reggae##1
10. the person traveling to london is on the right of the british##1
11. the turkish is on the left or right of the fan of r&b##3
12. the british is somewhere to the right of the australian##5
13. the fan of reggae is not to the left of the person traveling to london##8
14. the australian is the person traveling to marseilles##1
15. the australian is not the person who's sport is ice-hockey##6

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2     |      3      |    4    |
| Nationality         | american     | australian   | british | turkish |
| Music-Genre   | disco | electronic   | r&b   | reggae  |
| Sport         | ice-hockey  | lacrosse  | water-polo  | cycling |
| City     | colone    | marseilles | berlin     | london    |

