.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-8-2::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: romance, sports, fantasy, epic
There 4 different types of food: carrot, grapes, kale, peas
The people have 4 different jobs:  social-worker, scientist, electrician, mechanic
The people have 4 different hobbies: gardening, photography, rock-climbing, card-games
 1. the electrician is between the person who's hobby is gardening and the scientist##2
 2. the person watching sports movies is not to the right of the person who's hobby is photography##8
 3. the person watching sports movies is on the left or right of the person eating carrot##3
 4. the person watching romance movies is not to the right of the person who's hobby is card-games##8
 5. the person who's hobby is gardening is not to the left of the scientist##8
 6. the person eating peas is not to the right of the person watching epic movies##8
 7. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is somewhere to the left of the person who's hobby is card-games##5
 8. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is in an odd position##4
 9. the social-worker is the person who's hobby is photography##1
10. the electrician is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is gardening##3
11. the person who's hobby is gardening is not to the left of the electrician##8
12. the person watching epic movies is on the left of the person watching sports movies##1
13. the mechanic is somewhere to the right of the person eating grapes##5
14. the scientist is on the left or right of the electrician##3
15. the person watching romance movies is on the far left or far right##3
16. the person eating kale is on the right of the person eating carrot##1
17. the person watching romance movies is not to the right of the scientist##8
18. the person eating grapes is not to the right of the person who's hobby is photography##8
19. the person watching epic movies is on the right of the person eating grapes##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |   2    |   3    |   4   |
| Movie-Genre      | romance | fantasy | epic  | sports  |
| Food          | peas     | grapes | carrot | kale  |
| Job   | scientist    | electrician  | mechanic | social-worker |
| Hobby           | rock-climbing | card-games | gardening    | photography  |

