 3. the victorian house is somewhere to the left of the oliveros-smoker##5
 4. the futuristic house is somewhere to the right of the fan of blues##5
 5. the person playing billiard is not to the right of the prince-smoker##8
 6. the victorian house is not to the left of the ritmeester-smoker##8
 7. the fan of folk is in an odd position##4
 8. the ritmeester-smoker is on the left of the oliveros-smoker##1
 9. the oliveros-smoker is on the left of the swisher-smoker##1
10. the person playing chess is on the far right##1
11. the prince-smoker is not to the left of the fan of electronic##8
12. the oliveros-smoker is on the left or right of the person playing chess##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2     |     3     |     4      |
