 4. the person watching martial-arts movies is between the person traveling to edinburgh and the person traveling to san-francisco##2
 5. the person driving the car is on the left or right of the person who's sport is basketball##3
 6. the person who's sport is basketball is not to the right of the person watching martial-arts movies##8
