10. the person traveling to san-francisco is the person who's sport is basketball##1
11. the person who's sport is golf is not to the right of the person watching crime movies##8
12. the person traveling to edinburgh is on the left or right of the person who's sport is golf##3
13. the person driving the car is on the right of the person driving the taxi##1
14. the person traveling to san-francisco is on the left or right of the person who's sport is golf##3
