 2. the owner of the goldfish is the person who's birthday is in july##1
 3. the person who likes grey is not the person who's birthday is in may##6
 4. the person who likes coral is on the left of the person watching mystery movies##1
 5. the person watching disaster movies is not to the right of the owner of the goat##8
 6. the person who likes red is not to the right of the person watching disaster movies##8
 7. the person who likes grey is not to the left of the person who's birthday is in july##8
 8. the owner of the ferret is the person watching drama movies##1
 9. the owner of the fish is not to the left of the person who's birthday is in september##8
10. the person watching mystery movies is not to the left of the person watching disaster movies##8
11. the person who likes blue is between the person who's birthday is in september and the person watching drama movies##2
12. the person who's birthday is in may is on the right of the person who likes red##1
13. the owner of the ferret is not to the right of the person watching drama movies##8
14. the person who likes grey is on the left or right of the person watching drama movies##3

.:: Answer ::.
