 7. the person who's sport is skiing is not to the left of the person who's sport is water-polo##8
 8. the person who's sport is volleyball is somewhere between the person who growspoppy and the person who growsaconite##7
 9. the person eating avocado is on the far left or far right##3
10. the person eating carrot is not to the left of the person eating carrot##8
11. the person eating avocado is on the far left##1
12. the person eating kale is on the far right##1
13. the person who's sport is skiing is the person who growspoppy##1
