.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2       |     3     |    4    |
| Job           | fisherman | doctor       | chef      | writer  |
| Beverage   | lemonade    | water | coffee   | mirinda   |
| Game   | billiard   | poker          | monopoly      | scrabble  |
| City   | prague   | marseilles      | boston | miami |

