.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-8-16::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: coffee, iced-tea, mirinda, water
There are 4 different favourite colors: lavender, purple, emerald, light-blue
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: animation, western, time-travel, epic
House: victorian, ranch-style, futuristic, art-deco
 1. the person drinking mirinda is the person watching epic movies##1
 2. the ranch-style house is on the right of the art-deco house##1
 3. the person drinking iced-tea is somewhere to the right of the art-deco house##5
 4. the person drinking coffee is on the far left##1
 5. the victorian house is on the left or right of the person who likes light-blue##3
 6. the futuristic house is on the left or right of the person who likes emerald##3
 7. the person drinking iced-tea is on the left or right of the person drinking mirinda##3
 8. the ranch-style house is not to the right of the person watching western movies##8
 9. the victorian house is on the left of the person watching time-travel movies##1
10. the person drinking iced-tea is not to the right of the person who likes purple##8
11. the person who likes emerald is on the right of the person drinking water##1
12. the art-deco house is in an odd position##4
13. the person who likes emerald is somewhere to the left of the person watching western movies##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |     3      |    4     |
| Beverage      | coffee   | water     | mirinda    | iced-tea |
| Color   | lavender  | light-blue      | emerald     | purple     |
| Movie-Genre         | animation | time-travel  | epic     | western  |
| House     | victorian     | futuristic | art-deco | ranch-style     |

