.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-8-17::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: october, may, november, march
The people have 4 different jobs:  teacher, videographer, journalist, paramedic
City: liverpool, boston, san-francisco, rome
There are 4 different nationalities: brazilian, british, german, italian
