 2. the person who's birthday is in october is not to the right of the paramedic##8
 3. the person who's birthday is in march is the person traveling to boston##1
 4. the person traveling to boston is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in october##3
 5. the person who's birthday is in may is somewhere to the right of the person traveling to rome##5
 6. the journalist is not to the left of the person traveling to liverpool##8
 7. the person who's birthday is in november is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in may##3
 8. the person traveling to liverpool is on the left or right of the german##3
 9. the british is not to the left of the paramedic##8
10. the person traveling to san-francisco is not the brazilian##6
11. the videographer is on the left of the teacher##1
12. the italian is on the left of the person who's birthday is in november##1
13. the person traveling to rome is not to the right of the paramedic##8
14. the brazilian is on the right of the person traveling to san-francisco##1

.:: Answer ::.
