The people have 4 different hobbies: traveling, puzzles, rock-climbing, fishing
 1. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is on the left or right of the turkish##3
 2. the owner of the snake is not to the right of the person watching family movies##8
 3. the owner of the goat is the dutch##1
 4. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is on the left of the owner of the snake##1
 5. the dutch is somewhere to the right of the owner of the pony##5
 6. the person who's hobby is fishing is the italian##1
 7. the person watching zombie movies is not to the right of the person who's hobby is fishing##8
 8. the person watching satire movies is on the far right##1
 9. the person watching family movies is not to the right of the turkish##8
10. the person who's hobby is traveling is on the far right##1
11. the owner of the goat is somewhere to the left of the owner of the snake##5
12. the owner of the pony is somewhere to the left of the owner of the hedgehog##5
13. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is not to the left of the person watching zombie movies##8

