 4. the dancer is not to the left of the mexican##8
 5. the fisherman is somewhere to the right of the photographer##5
 6. the person who's birthday is in july is on the far left or far right##3
 7. the polish is somewhere to the left of the person eating tomato##5
 8. the person eating avocado is not to the left of the photographer##8
 9. the person eating cherry is on the left or right of the colombian##3
10. the person eating pear is somewhere between the person who's birthday is in march and the project-manager##7
11. the person who's birthday is in july is on the left of the person eating pear##1

