.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-8-20::.
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: montecristo, vegafina, cain, aristoff
There are 4 different favourite beverages: coffee, water, lemonade, soy-milk
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: adventure, animation, romance, western
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: parkour, rowing, badminton, golf
 1. the aristoff-smoker is not to the left of the person drinking coffee##8
 2. the cain-smoker is on the right of the person watching romance movies##1
 3. the person who's sport is golf is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is badminton##5
 4. the person drinking soy-milk is the person watching western movies##1
 5. the cain-smoker is not the person drinking lemonade##6
 6. the person watching adventure movies is not to the right of the person who's sport is rowing##8
 7. the person watching animation movies is not to the left of the person drinking lemonade##8
 8. the person drinking lemonade is on the left or right of the vegafina-smoker##3
 9. the person who's sport is badminton is in an even position##4
10. the person watching adventure movies is on the left or right of the person who's sport is rowing##3
11. the person watching adventure movies is in an even position##4
12. the cain-smoker is between the person drinking lemonade and the aristoff-smoker##2
13. the aristoff-smoker is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2     |       3       |     4      |
| Cigar         | aristoff    | cain   | montecristo   | vegafina |
| Beverage           | coffee | water    | lemonade | soy-milk    |
| Movie-Genre   | romance   | adventure | animation     | western    |
| Sport   | parkour   | badminton      | rowing         | golf     |

 